@startuml
' Embedded standalone style block (replicated per file; standalone)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 3
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

autonumber "<b>"

actor "Personal Logistico\n(rol staff)" as Staff
actor "Administrador\n(rol admin)" as Admin
boundary "Angular Admin\n(inventory / Apollo)" as Boundary
control "Inventory resolvers\n(mutations.go / resolvers)" as Resolvers
entity "InventoryEntry\n(inventory.go - InventoryRepo)" as Repo
database "NeonDB\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

== Consulta de existencias por sucursal (Personal Logistico / Administrador) ==
Staff -> Boundary : Abrir modulo de inventario\n(filtrar por sucursal / bajo stock)
Boundary -> Resolvers : query inventoryEntries\n(filter, limit, offset) (POST /graphql)
Resolvers -> Resolvers : requireAuth\n(admin / staff)
Resolvers -> Repo : SearchInventory(filter)
Repo -> DB : SELECT inventory por\nSC-01 / SC-02 (quantity, reorder_level)
DB --> Repo : filas de inventario por sucursal
Repo --> Resolvers : InventoryPage
Resolvers -> Resolvers : Evaluar bajo stock\n(quantity <= reorder_level)
Resolvers --> Boundary : Entradas + alertas de reposicion
Boundary --> Staff : Mostrar stock por sucursal\n(resaltar bajo punto de reorden)

== Ajuste de existencias multisucursal (Personal Logistico / Administrador) ==
Admin -> Boundary : Fijar / ajustar stock o\npunto de reorden (variant, branch)
Boundary -> Resolvers : mutation setInventoryStock /\nadjustInventoryStock /\nupdateInventoryReorderLevel /\nupsertInventory

alt rol no autorizado (requireAdmin/Staff falla)
  Resolvers --> Boundary : error no autorizado
  Boundary --> Admin : Mostrar error de permisos
else rol autorizado
  alt setInventoryStock (cantidad absoluta)
    Resolvers -> Repo : SetStock(variantId, branchId, quantity)
    Repo -> DB : INSERT ... ON CONFLICT\nUPDATE quantity
  else adjustInventoryStock (delta firmado)
    Resolvers -> Repo : AdjustStock(variantId, branchId, delta)
    Repo -> DB : UPDATE quantity = quantity + delta\n(no baja de cero)
  else updateInventoryReorderLevel (umbral)
    Resolvers -> Repo : SetReorderLevel(variantId, branchId, level)
    Repo -> DB : UPDATE reorder_level
  else upsertInventory (alta / sincronizacion)
    Resolvers -> Repo : Upsert(variantId, branchId, quantity, reorderLevel)
    Repo -> DB : INSERT ... ON CONFLICT UPDATE\nquantity + reorder_level
  end

  alt escritura exitosa
    DB --> Repo : fila (quantity, reorder_level, updated_at)
    Repo --> Resolvers : InventoryEntry
    Resolvers -> Resolvers : Reevaluar bajo stock\n(quantity <= reorder_level)
    Resolvers --> Boundary : InventoryEntry + estado de reposicion
    Boundary --> Admin : Refrescar tablero de inventario
  else error de persistencia (p.ej. delta invalido)
    DB --> Repo : error
    Repo --> Resolvers : error
    Resolvers --> Boundary : error de operacion
    Boundary --> Admin : Mostrar error al usuario
  end
end
@enduml
